{"word":"G3796 - ὀψέ - opsé - op-seh' - Even","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀψέ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">opsé</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">op-seh'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Even</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"சாயங்காலத்தில் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"late in the day"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G3694 - ὀπίσω - opísō - op-is'-o/3694\">G3694</a> (through the idea of <i>backwardness</i>); (adverbially) <i>late</i> in the day; by extension <i>after the close</i> of the day: - (at) even, in the end.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}